eight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1></span></div><div data-rid="442d063a-6ffb-439c-ad7c-784004e67475" class="r-1s0p45z" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="36a84af5-222c-4546-9251-8edbf501973d" class="r-ik4wh1" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="536aaa72-4f4f-47a8-93db-d0a0fb5e86e0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-g81ppv"><div data-rid="28413ed4-308f-48b7-9581-ebf3d813f35c" class="r-1ynivqy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What are the ingredients in Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="6a512cbc-de54-420c-a46c-8fbf70022127" class="r-rk75o4" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1k6na7e" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R3br2:"><div data-rid="c9aef892-c732-4f69-b053-f700c0deb557" class="r-q4fcsn"><div data-rid="fd8f435f-3d54-4a0f-a4d8-b71769192a5a" class="r-59g27t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia’s Sleep Spray is made with a clean blend of natural, science-backed ingredients that help you fall asleep faster, stay asleep longer, and wake up clear. Each serving includes melatonin to support your body’s natural sleep cycle, 5-HTP to promote relaxation and mood balance, and a proprietary blend of calming herbs like passionflower, valerian, lemon balm, chamomile, hops, and magnolia bark. These ingredients work together to calm your nervous system, lower stress, and support deep, restorative sleep. Rejuvia is non-habit forming, gentle on your body, and made with natural peppermint flavor and clean ingredients.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="760df8e2-cdc2-4ddb-a576-1ea35c10d2d1" class="r-1j18d1v" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d2c06e80-df5a-43c3-9a10-d6ff94c51675" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-vgn4xy"><div data-rid="7d0843b6-0231-4673-9300-d40db15cf96d" class="r-ajw0hd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How long does one spray last?</p></span></div><div data-rid="42e86cc3-0a78-45f6-ba49-8fdab0d2fcc7" class="r-h13c1v" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1cglsqg" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5br2:"><div data-rid="1eac77ff-0b5f-4a26-9c78-59ebf66197dd" class="r-hmcujy"><div data-rid="e4ddbf36-9022-407e-a40b-edd9742dcead" class="r-1p3irlt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One bottle of Rejuvia typically lasts about 30 nights when used as directed. Most people use 6 to 8 sprays before bed, which delivers the ideal amount for fast, deep, and consistent sleep. Because the spray absorbs so efficiently through your mouth, you don’t need large doses to feel the effects. It’s designed to fit seamlessly into your nightly routine — quick, simple, and long-lasting.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4ebb0578-51bb-458e-839e-503c6c04b6d7" class="r-a1gdft" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="78c51b07-8b47-4407-ae8b-5819bdb99696" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-j2368w"><div data-rid="ae13d795-c823-4673-ba72-86cd2e423126" class="r-9ccsi7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will Rejuvia make me feel groggy?</p></span></div><div data-rid="8f185fa5-add9-437f-adb4-5808d903a2f6" class="r-1168wz8" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-q8onpd" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R7br2:"><div data-rid="e5e8ff29-a1a5-42ac-a3fc-64ef06682f9c" class="r-n55zlt"><div data-rid="e4ac1077-c205-4351-b596-ac050dc494b6" class="r-eisj0t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia won’t make you feel groggy or heavy the next morning. It’s designed to help your body relax naturally instead of forcing you into sedation like many sleeping pills do. The ingredients are gentle and clean, working with your body’s own rhythms so you can fall asleep faster, stay asleep longer, and wake up feeling clear and refreshed. Most people say they wake up feeling calm, focused, and ready to start their day — not sluggish or foggy.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="efc08261-ad47-44d0-a242-788300f6e69b" class="r-7ygetm" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="1968ca62-65f7-42b8-b684-86e7b2a189b0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R9br2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1rib5ew"><div data-rid="979809e4-56af-466d-b70c-673c5e568d24" class="r-1r6wrtb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is Rejuvia safe to use long-term?</p></span></div><div data-rid="d8a97a01-cde0-4201-af44-dfef7698ba57" class="r-1ts5249" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-16e4qkq" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R9br2:"><div data-rid="f8db0c58-5fb0-4a58-af5c-694ed87322d2" class="r-w6n6zq"><div data-rid="136f6031-c414-4c53-bcc4-5302151ad364" class="r-ft1cly alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. The sprays are non-habit forming, all-natural, and safe for nightly use. There’s no dependency or “getting used to it” — just consistent, restorative sleep over time.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="6fdc92be-818b-4be4-a7cc-4faf8a9787d9" class="r-o0wne0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="12fc2128-e158-4a77-a5a0-b02ac9ecab00" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rbbr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-9fkom5"><div data-rid="4f678417-9fd5-461e-acfa-3c247c2e075f" class="r-j3uh9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Does Rejuvia have side effects?</p></span></div><div data-rid="e8a4fe40-b9aa-408e-a3d7-32e4f462aac4" class="r-1bee6c7" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-d1whcg" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rbbr2:"><div data-rid="7849689f-1222-4dc8-8a23-def7f46c0cfd" class="r-1lqf